<text><body>
<lb n="0190b15"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0190b16"/>
<lb n="0190b17"/><head type="no">No. 949</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0190b18"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0190039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】東寺三密藏古寫本，【甲】石山寺藏古寫本</note>奇特最勝金輪佛頂念誦儀軌法
<lb n="0190b19"/>要</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0190b20"/>
<lb n="0190b21"/><p>夫欲修習一字頂輪王法者。先須入大曼荼羅
<lb n="0190b22"/>海會。從師親<note n="0190040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受＝授【甲】</note><app n="0190040"><lem>受</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">授</rdg></app>灌頂。既蒙印可方得諮。學微
<lb n="0190b23"/>妙軌則真言教門。建立道場。一依本部儀式。
<lb n="0190b24"/>畫本尊像。如法安置。若欲疾成悉地。先須沐
<lb n="0190b25"/>浴。著新淨衣。若出家者。精持律儀。不得缺
<lb n="0190b26"/>犯。若在家者。應受近住八支淨戒。復當殷重
<lb n="0190b27"/>發廣大心。於阿闍梨所敬仰如佛。愍諸有情
<lb n="0190b28"/>起大悲願。不惜身命常生濟度。悉令離苦獲
<lb n="0190b29"/>大利樂。入道場已。五輪投地。虔誠<note n="0190041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">普＝並【甲】</note><app n="0190041"><lem>普</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">並</rdg></app>禮一切
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0949.0190c" n="0190c"/>
<lb n="0190c01"/>如來。復對本尊。&M010527;沙聖眾以淨三業悔除罪
<lb n="0190c02"/>障。勸請諸佛轉妙法輪。隨喜三乘所修福智。
<lb n="0190c03"/>以斯妙善迴向菩提。法界眾生同階佛果</p>
<lb n="0190c04"/><p>次以塗香塗手。合掌如蓮。觀察本源。自性清
<lb n="0190c05"/>淨。為諸客塵之所覆蔽。作此觀已。運心廣布。
<lb n="0190c06"/>我與眾生亦同清淨。為令清淨故。誦此殊勝。
<lb n="0190c07"/><note n="0190042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">浴澡＝澡浴【甲】</note><app n="0190042"><lem>浴澡</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">澡浴</rdg></app>真<note n="0190043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＋（曰）【甲】</note><app n="0190043"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">言曰</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0190c08"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>薩<note n="0190044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＝縛【甲】＊</note><app n="0190044"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>婆<note place="inline">去</note><anchor id="fxT19p0190c01"/>&CB00085;&CB02122;<note place="inline">詩律反</note>度唅</p>
<lb n="0190c09"/><p>由三誦明故。身口意三業乃至遍法界一切
<lb n="0190c10"/>悉清淨</p>
<lb n="0190c11"/><p>次結一切諸佛部心三昧耶印</p>
<lb n="0190c12"/><p>止觀十度內叉拳。禪智二度並申合。遍觀諸
<lb n="0190c13"/>佛滿虛空。三誦真言頂上散。諸佛部心真言
<lb n="0190c14"/>曰</p>
<lb n="0190c15"/><p type="dharani">唵<note n="0190045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一〕－【甲】</note><app n="0190045"><lem><note place="inline">一</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>爾曩爾迦<note place="inline">半字呼</note>娑<anchor id="fxT19p0190c02"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀<note n="0190046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0190046"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0190c16"/><p>由結前印誦真言故。十方諸佛一切如來。承
<lb n="0190c17"/>本誓願。皆悉運集。遍滿虛空。舒光照燭。加
<lb n="0190c18"/>持行人。離諸障惱。三業清淨。速證菩提</p>
<lb n="0190c19"/><p>次結一切諸菩薩蓮華部心三昧耶印</p>
<lb n="0190c20"/><lg><l>准前結佛部心印</l><l><note n="0190047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">屈左＝次屈【甲】</note><app n="0190047"><lem>屈左</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">次屈</rdg></app>智度入掌中</l>
<lb n="0190c21"/><l>禪度直&CB00594;或三招</l><l>運心憶<note n="0190048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">念＝仰【甲】</note><app n="0190048"><lem>念</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">仰</rdg></app>觀自在</l>
<lb n="0190c22"/><l>一切微塵菩薩眾</l><l>持蓮眷屬滿空中</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0949.0191a" n="0191a"/>
<lb n="0191a01"/><l>至心三遍誦真言</l><l>方以印於頂右散</l></lg>
<lb n="0191a02"/><p>蓮華部心真言曰</p>
<lb n="0191a03"/><p type="dharani">唵阿<note place="inline">去</note>嚕力迦<note place="inline">半字呼</note>娑<anchor id="fxT19p0191a01"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note><note n="0191001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀＋（引）細註【甲】＊</note><app n="0191001"><lem>賀</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">賀<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0191a04"/><p>由結前印誦真言故。觀自在菩薩承本誓願。
<lb n="0191a05"/>將<note n="0191002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諸＋（持）【甲】</note><app n="0191002"><lem>諸</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">諸持</rdg></app>蓮華眾無量菩薩。遍滿虛空。皆悉運
<lb n="0191a06"/>集。放大光明。加持行者。令得清淨。所求滿
<lb n="0191a07"/>足。離諸障難。疾證菩提</p>
<lb n="0191a08"/><p>次結一切金剛部心三昧耶印</p>
<lb n="0191a09"/><p>准前復結佛部心印</p>
<lb n="0191a10"/><lg><l>屈右禪度入掌中</l><l>智度直&CB00594;或三<note n="0191003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">次下甲本有遍想金剛藏王眾一句</note>招</l>
<lb n="0191a11"/><l>塵沙眷屬共圍繞</l><l>威光赫奕遍虛空</l>
<lb n="0191a12"/><l>至誠三遍誦真言</l><l>方以印於頂左散</l></lg>
<lb n="0191a13"/><p>金剛部心真言曰</p>
<lb n="0191a14"/><p type="dharani">唵<anchor id="fxT19p0191a02"/>&CB00085;日羅<note place="inline">二合</note>地力<note place="inline">二合</note>迦<note place="inline">半字呼</note>娑縛<note place="inline">二合</note>賀<anchor id="fxT19p0191a03"/><note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0191a15"/><p>由結前印誦真言故。十方一切金剛手等承
<lb n="0191a16"/>本願因。如雲而集。現大威德。加持行人。除障
<lb n="0191a17"/>摧魔。自在無礙。疾成悉地。速至菩提</p>
<lb n="0191a18"/><p>次結金剛甲冑護身印</p>
<lb n="0191a19"/><lg><l>止觀羽作金剛拳</l><l>禪智橫屈於掌內</l>
<lb n="0191a20"/><l>進力如鉤慣甲勢</l><l>加持心額二肩喉</l>
<lb n="0191a21"/><l>至<note n="0191004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">心＝誠【甲】</note><app n="0191004"><lem>心</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">誠</rdg></app>三遍誦真言</l><l>印身五處頂上散</l></lg>
<lb n="0191a22"/><p>甲冑護身真言曰</p>
<lb n="0191a23"/><p type="dharani">唵<note n="0191005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB03514;＝部【甲】</note><app n="0191005"><lem>&CB03514;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">部</rdg></app>入<anchor id="fxT19p0191a04"/>&CB00085;&CB00256;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00292;</p>
<lb n="0191a24"/><p>由結甲印誦真言故。加持五處。成大護身。即
<lb n="0191a25"/>同金剛堅固之體。金剛藏王承本願力。領諸
<lb n="0191a26"/>眷屬。數如塵沙無量金剛圍遶侍從。光明熾
<lb n="0191a27"/>盛。現忿怒形。加持行人。威德自在。辟除作
<lb n="0191a28"/>障。摧壞諸魔。小則能護一身。大則護持國界。
<lb n="0191a29"/>一切災厄。水火刀兵。毒藥<note n="0191006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蠱＝毒虫【甲】</note><app n="0191006"><lem>蠱</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">毒虫</rdg></app>虎狼猛獸。皆
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0949.0191b" n="0191b"/>
<lb n="0191b01"/>悉遠離不敢視之。毘那藥迦自然怖走。永無
<lb n="0191b02"/>惱害。疾證菩提</p>
<lb n="0191b03"/><p>次結辨<note n="0191007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">事＋（辟除）【甲】</note><app n="0191007"><lem>事</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">事辟除</rdg></app>印</p>
<lb n="0191b04"/><lg><l>止觀二羽內叉拳</l><l>禪智雙屈入掌中</l>
<lb n="0191b05"/><l>然申忍願頭相跓</l><l>頂上三旋成結護</l>
<lb n="0191b06"/><l>左轉三匝是辟除</l><l>隨心所到作方隅</l>
<lb n="0191b07"/><l>破法能成一切事</l></lg>
<lb n="0191b08"/><p>辨事佛頂真言曰</p>
<lb n="0191b09"/><p type="dharani">曩莫三<note place="inline">去</note>漫多母馱南<note place="inline">引</note>唵拏嚕唵<note place="inline">二合</note>滿馱娑
<lb n="0191b10"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note><anchor id="fxT19p0191b01"/>賀</p>
<lb n="0191b11"/><p>由結前印及誦真言。悉能辟除及結護界。是
<lb n="0191b12"/>名諸佛警悟聖心。能破他法。壞滅魔羅。天龍
<lb n="0191b13"/>八部。羅剎藥叉。毘那夜迦。忙怖奔走。由結此
<lb n="0191b14"/>印。世出世間一切事業速能成<corr sic="辨">辦</corr>。自在無礙。
<lb n="0191b15"/>悉地現前</p>
<lb n="0191b16"/><p>次結奉獻閼伽印</p>
<lb n="0191b17"/><p>二羽仰掌<note n="0191008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">捨＝捧【甲】</note><app n="0191008"><lem>捨</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">捧</rdg></app>器形</p>
<lb n="0191b18"/><lg><l>進力屈於忍願傍</l><l>禪智曲補於進力</l>
<lb n="0191b19"/><l>捧器三旋當額上</l><l>想浴聖眾淨如蓮</l></lg>
<lb n="0191b20"/><p>閼伽浴聖真言曰</p>
<lb n="0191b21"/><p type="dharani">曩麼三<note place="inline">去</note>滿多母馱南<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00344;&CB00344;曩糝魔沙麼娑
<lb n="0191b22"/><anchor id="fxT19p0191b02"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0191b23"/><p>由結此印誦真言奉獻閼伽浴聖故。表<note n="0191009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">修＝滌【甲】</note><app n="0191009"><lem>修</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">滌</rdg></app>行
<lb n="0191b24"/>人無始垢業蕩除清淨。如妙蓮華。當來果獲
<lb n="0191b25"/>得無染智</p>
<lb n="0191b26"/><p>次結虛空普供印</p>
<lb n="0191b27"/><lg><l>二羽合掌交初分</l><l>右押左縛如金剛</l>
<lb n="0191b28"/><l>想成真實微妙供</l><l>無量雲海奉聖眾</l>
<lb n="0191b29"/><l>供養一切諸如來</l><l>後說四句妙伽他</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0949.0191c" n="0191c"/>
<lb n="0191c01"/><l>五誦真言頂上散</l></lg><p>虛空大明真言曰</p>
<lb n="0191c02"/><p type="dharani">曩莫三滿多沒馱南<note place="inline">引</note>薩<anchor id="fxT19p0191c01"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>他<anchor id="fxT19p0191c02"/><note place="inline">引</note>欠<note n="0191010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盟＝&CB14002;【甲】</note><app n="0191010"><lem>盟</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB14002;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0191c03"/>娜孽帝薩頗<note place="inline">二合</note>囉呬&CB00805;&CB00344;&CB00344;曩劍娑<anchor id="fxT19p0191c03"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合<anchor id="fxT19p0191c04"/>引</note>
<lb n="0191c04"/>賀</p>
<lb n="0191c05"/><p>由結此印誦真言故。以不思議力。從<note n="0191011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">印流出乃至明照一切三百四十字甲本欠</note><note n="0191011" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>〔印流出…明照一切〕三百四十字－【甲】</note>印流出
<lb n="0191c06"/>一切供養。無量天眾各持天寶器。盛諸妙供
<lb n="0191c07"/>養。塞滿虛空所謂塗香燒燈。飲食衣服。幢蓋
<lb n="0191c08"/>瓔珞。奉獻如來誦一遍故。流出塗香。當來獲
<lb n="0191c09"/>得戒品塗香。誦二遍故。流出焚香。當來獲得
<lb n="0191c10"/>定芬馥。誦三遍故。流出花鬘。當來獲得離染
<lb n="0191c11"/>妙蓮。誦四遍故。流出寶食。當來獲得法喜禪
<lb n="0191c12"/>悅。誦五遍故。流出寶燈。當來獲得如來五眼。
<lb n="0191c13"/>當得如上諸功德波羅蜜門皆具足。復以心
<lb n="0191c14"/>遍法界。以誠實言誦妙伽他。而說偈言</p>
<lb n="0191c15"/><lg><l>以我功德力</l><l>如來加持力</l>
<lb n="0191c16"/><l>及以法界力</l><l>普供養而住</l></lg>
<lb n="0191c17"/><p>次以梵讚歌詠。本尊相好金身殊勝功德</p>
<lb n="0191c18"/><p type="dharani">麼禰史膩薩&CB00085;若&CB00344;<note place="inline">一</note>地帶史膩拽捨枲&CB00085;<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0191c19"/>合</note>&CB00576;<note place="inline">二</note>步嘌步晚禰迦滿馱<note place="inline">三</note>三麼娑多<note place="inline">二合</note>尾
<lb n="0191c20"/>&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>地跛<note place="inline">四</note>訖羅<note place="inline">二合</note>麼哩&CB00576;曩謨窣&CB00418;<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0191c21"/>合</note>帝怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>哆哩左訖羅<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">轉舌</note>底&CB00576;<note place="inline">六</note></p>
<lb n="0191c22"/><p>由讚佛三身。六根諸功德。八萬四千種。殊勝
<lb n="0191c23"/>不思議。承斯歌詠因。當來獲妙果。福聚海無
<lb n="0191c24"/>量。等同奇特尊</p>
<lb n="0191c25"/><p>次結佛眼大明印</p>
<lb n="0191c26"/><lg><l>止觀虛合未開敷</l><l>禪智雙屈在掌中</l>
<lb n="0191c27"/><l>進力各押忍願背</l><l>如眼開明照一切</l>
<lb n="0191c28"/><l>安<note n="0191012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">眉＝肩【甲】</note><app n="0191012"><lem>眉</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">肩</rdg></app>心額二肩喉</l><l>起大悲愍怖畏除</l></lg>
<lb n="0191c29"/><p>隨誦真言頂上散</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0949.0192a" n="0192a"/>
<lb n="0192a01"/><p>佛眼大明母真言曰</p>
<lb n="0192a02"/><p type="dharani">曩莫薩<anchor id="fxT19p0192a01"/>&CB00085;怛他<note place="inline">去引</note>蘗帝毘庾<note place="inline"><note n="0192001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（二合）＋引【甲】</note><app n="0192001"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">二合引</rdg></app>一</note>囉褐<note n="0192002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合二〕－【甲】</note><app n="0192002"><lem><note place="inline">二合二</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0192a03"/>毘藥<note place="inline">二<note n="0192003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＋（二）【甲】</note><app n="0192003"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">合二</rdg></app></note>三藐三沒弟毘藥<note place="inline">二合三</note>唵<note place="inline">四</note>嚕嚕窣
<lb n="0192a04"/><note n="0192004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">普嚕二合＝普二合嚕五【甲】</note><app n="0192004"><lem>普嚕<note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">普二合嚕五</rdg></app>入<anchor id="fxT19p0192a02"/>&CB00085;&CB00256;底<note place="inline">丁以反</note>瑟&CB00109;<note place="inline">二合六</note>悉馱路<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0192a05"/>左&CB00576;薩<anchor id="fxT19p0192a03"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0192005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00770;＝喇【甲】</note><app n="0192005"><lem>&CB00770;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">喇</rdg></app>他<note place="inline">二合去聲呼</note>娑<note place="inline">去</note>馱&CB00576;<note place="inline">八</note>娑<anchor id="fxT19p0192a04"/>&CB00085;
<lb n="0192a06"/><note place="inline">二合引</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0192a07"/><p>此名一切佛眼大明。能息可畏難調伏者。為
<lb n="0192a08"/>欲成就世間出世間一切佛頂大輪王法一切
<lb n="0192a09"/>事位滅諸諍論。亦是一切諸佛種族母。復是
<lb n="0192a10"/>一切諸大菩薩生養母。為說頂輪真言威德
<lb n="0192a11"/>奇特。諸大菩薩皆<note n="0192006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">失本心乃至證悉地三百十三字甲本欠</note><note n="0192006" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>失本心乃至證悉地三百十三字甲本欠</note>失本心。諸天龍神威力滅
<lb n="0192a12"/>沒。凡誦一字佛頂明。先須誦佛眼明。念誦畢
<lb n="0192a13"/>已。亦誦七遍。眾聖歡喜安樂有情</p>
<lb n="0192a14"/><p>次結一字根本印</p>
<lb n="0192a15"/><lg><l>止觀密縛內叉拳</l><l>由慼忍願如劍形</l>
<lb n="0192a16"/><l>禪智進力甲柱跓</l><l>是名金剛佛頂印</l>
<lb n="0192a17"/><l>想身威德同本尊</l><l>流光晃曜遍十方</l></lg>
<lb n="0192a18"/><p>印身五處頂上散</p>
<lb n="0192a19"/><p>金輪頂王真言曰</p>
<lb n="0192a20"/><p type="dharani">曩謨三漫多<note place="inline">一</note>母馱南<note place="inline">二</note>唵&CB00292;&CB03514;&CB01236;<note place="inline">二合彈舌重呼</note>&CB00292;</p>
<lb n="0192a21"/><lg><l>此是摩訶印</l><l>所謂如來頂</l>
<lb n="0192a22"/><l>由斯結誦故</l><l>即同於世尊</l>
<lb n="0192a23"/><l>演說頂輪明</l><l>三千六反動</l>
<lb n="0192a24"/><l>山河皆勇沸</l><l>大火遍魔宮</l>
<lb n="0192a25"/><l>惶怖盡歸依</l><l>地獄眾苦息</l>
<lb n="0192a26"/><l>菩薩龍天眾</l><l>畏仰如佛身</l></lg>
<lb n="0192a27"/><p>次結大慈普護印</p>
<lb n="0192a28"/><p>十度相叉作月形　禪智檀惠相著　印心額
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0949.0192b" n="0192b"/>
<lb n="0192b01"/>喉頂上散</p>
<lb n="0192b02"/><p>慈護真言曰</p>
<lb n="0192b03"/><p type="dharani">唵沒馱昧怛哩<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;曰囉<note place="inline">二合</note>洛乞灑<note place="inline">二合</note>憾</p>
<lb n="0192b04"/><lg><l>結印誦明除怖畏</l><l>起大悲心遍一切</l>
<lb n="0192b05"/><l>所有怨敵惡相淩</l><l>願彼皆當大安樂</l>
<lb n="0192b06"/><l>由此三誦悲護故</l><l>毒害之心自覺悟</l>
<lb n="0192b07"/><l>深生悔過向菩提</l><l>歡喜敬仰前人所</l>
<lb n="0192b08"/><l>初後若常誦此明</l><l>惶怖眾生得安慰</l>
<lb n="0192b09"/><l>護大利益殊勝事</l><l>速滿諸願證悉地</l></lg>
<lb n="0192b10"/><p>次結淨珠印</p>
<lb n="0192b11"/><lg><l>盤珠於掌內</l><l>如蓮未開形<note n="0192007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">甲本有進力屈上節一句</note><note n="0192007" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>甲本有進力屈上節一句</note></l>
<lb n="0192b12"/><l>捧合於心上</l><l>三七遍加持</l>
<lb n="0192b13"/><l>頂戴慇重心</l><l>如法而供養</l></lg>
<lb n="0192b14"/><p>淨珠真言曰</p>
<lb n="0192b15"/><p type="dharani">唵阿<note n="0192008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB03315;&CB03514;＝納部【甲】</note><app n="0192008"><lem>&CB03315;&CB03514;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">納部</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合<anchor id="fxT19p0192b01"/>引</note>帝&CB03494;惹曳<note place="inline">而異反</note>悉地<note place="inline">引</note>悉馱<note n="0192009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00770;二合＝賴【甲】</note><app n="0192009"><lem>&CB00770;
<lb n="0192b16"/><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">賴</rdg></app>剃娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合<anchor id="fxT19p0192b02"/><anchor id="fxT19p0192b03"/>引</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0192b17"/><p>次結持數印</p>
<lb n="0192b18"/><lg><l>二羽半金剛</l><l>禪智捻戒方</l>
<lb n="0192b19"/><l>進力忍願後<note place="inline">屈不相著</note></l><l>七遍持<note n="0192010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">數＝珠【甲】</note><app n="0192010"><lem>數</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">珠</rdg></app>明</l></lg>
<lb n="0192b20"/><p>然後而念誦</p>
<lb n="0192b21"/><p>持珠真言曰</p>
<lb n="0192b22"/><p type="dharani">曩莫婆&CB00344;<anchor id="fxT19p0192b04"/>&CB00085;帝蘇悉地娑馱也娑馱也娑馱
<lb n="0192b23"/>囉剃娑<anchor id="fxT19p0192b05"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合<anchor id="fxT19p0192b06"/>引</note><anchor id="fxT19p0192b07"/>賀</p>
<lb n="0192b24"/><lg><l>先當淨三業</l><l>加法而念誦</l>
<lb n="0192b25"/><l>一心莫散亂</l><l><note n="0192011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">注＝住【甲】</note><app n="0192011"><lem>注</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">住</rdg></app>想於本尊</l>
<lb n="0192b26"/><l>字句分明呼</l><l>不緩亦不急</l>
<lb n="0192b27"/><l>勿生懈怠意</l><l><note n="0192012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聲咳及頻申＝&CB14024;吹及&CB12472;呻【甲】</note><app n="0192012"><lem>聲咳及頻申</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB14024;吹及&CB12472;呻</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0192b28"/><l>雜染縱惛沈</l><l>如是諸過咎</l>
<lb n="0192b29"/><l>少分生<note n="0192013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">忘＝妄【明】</note><app n="0192013"><lem>忘</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">妄</rdg></app>緣</l><l>皆不得成就</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0949.0192c" n="0192c"/>
<lb n="0192c01"/><l>念誦課數畢</l><l>持珠安舊處</l>
<lb n="0192c02"/><l>方入三昧耶</l><l><note n="0192014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當＝常【甲】</note><app n="0192014"><lem>當</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">常</rdg></app>住本尊觀</l>
<lb n="0192c03"/><l>食頃從定出</l><l>&CB00230;結根本印</l>
<lb n="0192c04"/><l>次結佛眼明</l><l>歌詠音讚歎</l>
<lb n="0192c05"/><l>普供閼伽已</l><l>辟除左解散</l>
<lb n="0192c06"/><l>三部重護身</l><l>最後慈護印</l>
<lb n="0192c07"/><l>禮悔依前儀</l><l>讀誦大乘典</l>
<lb n="0192c08"/><l>隨意任經行</l><l>常時莫間斷</l></lg>
<lb n="0192c09"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>頂輪王<note n="0192015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">要略一卷＝念誦要略儀軌【甲】</note><app n="0192015"><lem>要略一卷</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">念誦要略儀軌</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0192c10"/><div2 type="other"><head><note n="0192016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以下甲本無之，此行原本朱書</note>奇特最勝金輪佛頂念誦儀軌法要</head>
<lb n="0192c11"/><p>若不能誦向前大佛眼真言誦此心真言亦得
<lb n="0192c12"/><note n="0192017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此行原本朱書</note>佛眼小&CB00057;也</p>
<lb n="0192c13"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&lac;</t><t lang="chi">曩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&lac;</t><t lang="chi">莫</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&lac;</t><t lang="chi">三</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&lac;</t><t lang="chi">滿</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&lac;</t><t lang="chi">多</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&lac;</t><t lang="chi">沒</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&lac;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>馱</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&lac;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>喃</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd"><note n="0192018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此陀羅尼梵字原本朱書</note>&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A65A;</t><t lang="chi">沒</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-AF72;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>馱</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A652;</t><t lang="chi">路</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A47C;</t><t lang="chi">左</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5AF;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>&CB00576;</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B065;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>娑&CB00085;</zi><sg>二合引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0192c14"/>
<lb n="0192c15"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi">賀</t></tt></p>
<lb n="0192c16"/>
<lb n="0192c17"/><p type="W" rend="margin-left:12"><note n="0192019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">教舜以下原本朱書</note><tt rend="inline"><t lang="chi">教舜</t><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E0EE;</t></tt></p>
<lb n="0192c18"/><p type="W" rend="margin-left:12">二交了</p></div2>
<lb n="0192c19"/><div2 type="other"><head>水壇法</head>
<lb n="0192c20"/><p>取新淨牛糞。不食糟豆特。犢子糞最第一。不
<lb n="0192c21"/>得直用其生牛糞。取新瓦鑵以汲淨水。不用
<lb n="0192c22"/>殘水。寫淨&CB03546;中。以糞和水。攪去其滓。著檀香
<lb n="0192c23"/>末。取一柳枝。以右手執。左手執金剛杵及其
<lb n="0192c24"/>數珠。東坐誦佛頂心&CB00057;。柳枝攪水。&CB00057;一百八
<lb n="0192c25"/>遍。持&CB00057;水器。入道場中。從東北角捕其香水。
<lb n="0192c26"/>以右手摩地。隨日轉摩。隨摩隨乾。勿令停水。
<lb n="0192c27"/>道場內地一編摩訖。乃至道場水四邊摩。各
<lb n="0192c28"/>一步地四角&CB00594;標結繩為界。此則名為佛頂
<lb n="0192c29"/>三昧陀羅尼結界之地。如一編摩。第二第三
<lb n="0192c30"/>亦如是摩。摩地不得用殘香水。日日別取新
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0949.0193a" n="0193a"/>
<lb n="0193a01"/>淨牛糞。准前作用。作此水者。則名佛頂三昧
<lb n="0193a02"/>陀羅尼八功德水壇地乾竟</p>
<lb n="0193a03"/><p type="W">　　　　　　　　　　　　　二校了</p></div2></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>
